General.Name: Selectirente
General.Description: Selectirente is a public real estate fund managed by Sofidy. It invests in city center and suburb commercial properties, which should be located close to shopping malls. It primarily acquires properties in France. As of March 29, 2019, Selectirente operates as a subsidiary of Tikehau Capital.
